dct_description_sm: Covers also portions of the Yukon and British Columbia.
Shows shipping routes, railroads and trails, drainage, etc., with some cities in red (as opposed to black) ink--indicating N.N. Co. locations.
Relief shown by hachures and spot heights.
Inset map: Map of Fairbanks Mining Dist. Scale [ca. 1:422,400].
